analysis.description:
RefundableCrowdsale.forwardFunds (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#346-352) sends eth to arbitrary user
	Dangerous calls:
	- wallet.transfer(weiAmount) (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#348-349)

Reentrancy in EthealPreSale.buyTokens (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#541-561):
	External calls:
	- buyTokens(_beneficiary,weiAmount) (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#552-553)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- softCapClose (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#555-556)
Crowdsale.token (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#116-117) is never initialized. It is used in:

Crowdsale.transferToken (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#164-170) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.generateTokens(beneficiary,tokens) (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#168)

HasNoTokens.extractTokens (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#267-279) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-token.transfer(_claimer,balance) (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#276)

EthealPreSale.finalization (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#599-618) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-ethealController.ethealToken().transfer(ethealController.SALE(),_balance.sub(tokenBalance)) (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#610-614)
	-ethealController.ethealToken().transfer(ethealController.SALE(),_balance) (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#617-618)

EthealPreSale.getContributors has external calls inside a loop:
	- _pending && vault.deposited(contributorsKeys[i]) > 0 || _claimed && vault.deposited(contributorsKeys[i]) == 0 (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol)

Reentrancy in EthealPreSale.finalization (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#599-618):
	External calls:
	- _balance = getHealBalance() (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#599-600)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- tokenBalance (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#617)
	- tokenSold (/unique_chucks/8/0x1a20c3581b6c9713498f3f9e9258fc452df13a8c.sol#605-606)
